242
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,227
And the next order.

243
00:09:55,294 --> 00:09:58,064
-Bong-sik's next order, Noodle Bong-sik.
-Noodle Bong-sik.

244
00:09:59,065 --> 00:10:01,033
Wait, I think I know what this means.

245
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:04,837
I've always loved noodles
since I was a kid.

246
00:10:04,904 --> 00:10:07,907
I don't care if it has broth or not.
Something made with noodles.

247
00:10:08,874 --> 00:10:12,578
And that's why I keep
all kinds of noodles at home.

248
00:10:12,645 --> 00:10:14,880
-He loves all kinds of noodles.
-So you love noodles.

249
00:10:14,947 --> 00:10:16,983
It's fine as long as it's not too spicy.

250
00:10:17,049 --> 00:10:18,918
I'm not a picky eater.

251
00:10:18,985 --> 00:10:20,519
-I see.
-Do you not eat spicy food?

252
00:10:20,586 --> 00:10:22,622
I do like spicy food,

253
00:10:22,688 --> 00:10:25,691
but I can't eat it when I'm out
because I sweat too much.

254
00:10:25,758 --> 00:10:27,760
I can eat it at home,
but not when I'm out.

255
00:10:27,827 --> 00:10:29,395
Let's find the contenders.

256
00:10:29,462 --> 00:10:32,131
The four of you can decide where to go.

257
00:10:32,198 --> 00:10:36,268
Shall we give the first choice
to those who have no stars?

258
00:10:36,335 --> 00:10:39,205
-Where is it? Oh, I don't have any.
-You don't have any.

259
00:10:39,271 --> 00:10:41,340
Those without a star can
make the first choice.

260
00:10:41,407 --> 00:10:43,976
Please don't feel too conscious.
Yes, Poong?

261
00:10:44,043 --> 00:10:45,344
I'll go with "Noodle Bong-sik."

262
00:10:45,411 --> 00:10:47,680
-Noodle Bong-sik.
-Yes.

263
00:10:47,747 --> 00:10:50,683
-That makes Chef Yeon-bok take the top.
-Yes.

264
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:52,918
