265
00:10:52,985 --> 00:10:54,520
-Yes, it's fine.
-Okay.

266
00:10:54,587 --> 00:10:56,088
I'll also compete

267
00:10:56,155 --> 00:10:59,892
-with actual decency and skills.
-You'll fight with your skills?

268
00:10:59,959 --> 00:11:01,260
Yes, also,

269
00:11:01,327 --> 00:11:04,864
I was hoping
to play against Chef Kang-rok.

270
00:11:04,930 --> 00:11:08,968
I wanted to fight him head-on
in a serious battle.

271
00:11:09,035 --> 00:11:12,038
It's a wonder that he can make
dishes that have a taste.

272
00:11:14,073 --> 00:11:16,409
I don't want to fight him.

273
00:11:16,475 --> 00:11:20,680
The no-star battle.
It's about time one of you wins a star.

274
00:11:20,746 --> 00:11:22,481
Poong is a better choice.

275
00:11:22,548 --> 00:11:24,717
-I crossed over to the dark side,
-Right.

276
00:11:24,784 --> 00:11:27,253
-so I should fight a strong opponent.
-A strong opponent.

277
00:11:27,319 --> 00:11:28,621
I'll fight Poong.

278
00:11:29,822 --> 00:11:31,991
-Poong was a stronger opponent?
-Yes.

279
00:11:32,058 --> 00:11:33,959
That doesn't seem to make sense, but okay.

280
00:11:34,026 --> 00:11:37,229
That means Chef Jong-won will go up.

281
00:11:37,296 --> 00:11:40,666
-This is a huge fight too.
-He'll fight Chef Yeon-bok.

282
00:11:40,733 --> 00:11:42,234
THE DOUBLE STAR VERSUS THE MASTER

283
00:11:42,301 --> 00:11:43,302
I look forward to this.

284
00:11:43,369 --> 00:11:44,437
Is that all right?

285
00:11:44,937 --> 00:11:46,672
I did some research

286
00:11:46,739 --> 00:11:48,441
