357
00:14:36,275 --> 00:14:39,211
-I'm not that bad.
-You aren't, right?

358
00:14:39,278 --> 00:14:40,379
-You know the difference.
-Yes.

359
00:14:40,446 --> 00:14:42,615
Okay, now. This is called pork.

360
00:14:42,681 --> 00:14:44,250
Come on. He knows the difference now.

361
00:14:44,316 --> 00:14:47,086
