362
00:14:47,152 --> 00:14:48,554
-Yes.
-It's lighter.

363
00:14:48,621 --> 00:14:50,990
-The lighter one is pork.
-Yes.

364
00:14:51,056 --> 00:14:52,091
Beef is in darker red.

365
00:14:52,157 --> 00:14:53,726
-Some may not know the difference.
-Right.

366
00:14:53,792 --> 00:14:55,494
Do you have a sweet tooth?

367
00:14:55,561 --> 00:14:58,163
-I had that with apples.
-Apples.

368
00:14:58,230 --> 00:15:00,599
-That was a fad too.
-That's a fad.

369
00:15:00,666 --> 00:15:02,935
Look at that. You follow all these trends.

370
00:15:03,002 --> 00:15:05,437
There was a fad
to eat apples with peanut butter.

371
00:15:05,504 --> 00:15:08,374
-And chocolate.
-Chocolate. Yes.

372
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,708
You do have a sweet tooth.

373
00:15:09,775 --> 00:15:11,810
I do, but I try to stay away from sweets.

374
00:15:11,877 --> 00:15:14,780
And I found facial masks

375
00:15:14,847 --> 00:15:17,383
