376
00:15:17,449 --> 00:15:18,484
-Hey, wait.
-Wait.

377
00:15:18,550 --> 00:15:20,619
-Was Bong-sik not allowed to do facials?
-He is.

378
00:15:20,686 --> 00:15:23,789
