-He was.

379
00:15:23,856 --> 00:15:24,857
You take care of your looks.

380
00:15:24,924 --> 00:15:26,692
So I bought those with regenerative cream.

381
00:15:26,759 --> 00:15:28,961
-To soothe your skin.
-He used these.

382
00:15:29,028 --> 00:15:30,195
What's this?

383
00:15:30,262 --> 00:15:33,999
When I was at a duck place in Miryang,

384
00:15:34,066 --> 00:15:37,569
