and gave me some liquor as a present.

385
00:15:37,636 --> 00:15:39,204
-I see.
-It's some homemade liquor.

386
00:15:39,271 --> 00:15:41,807
-And this?
-I got those two as presents.

387
00:15:41,874 --> 00:15:42,942
But you don't drink.

388
00:15:43,008 --> 00:15:46,712
Many people hold
such prejudice against him.

389
00:15:46,779 --> 00:15:49,848
But I see a bottle of soju.
Did you drink this?

390
00:15:49,915 --> 00:15:51,183
-Or…
-I used it to make this braise.

391
00:15:51,250 --> 00:15:53,619
Did you use it to braise?
It's for you to cook with.

392
00:15:53,686 --> 00:15:55,587
-He must cook often.
-I guess so.

393
00:15:55,654 --> 00:15:57,756
I see. Wait a moment.

394
00:15:57,823 --> 00:15:59,959
