for my guests to drink with their liquor.

400
00:16:11,737 --> 00:16:13,138
So this is for cooking, and…

401
00:16:13,205 --> 00:16:14,573
We got him.

402
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:16,575
-He got him.
-We got Bong-sik.

403
00:16:16,642 --> 00:16:18,110
-We got him.
-He had alcohol here too.

404
00:16:18,177 --> 00:16:20,779
My gosh, look at these.
These are soju bottles, right?

405
00:16:20,846 --> 00:16:22,948
-Yes.
-It's not just one.

406
00:16:23,015 --> 00:16:25,384
